•webkitSpeechRecognition is a browser-specific version 
of the Speech Recognition API
 used to convert voice (speech) into text.




•	lang = "en-US" → language is English 
•	continuous = false → listens only once (not continuously) 
•	interimResults = false → only final result (no partial text) 



•SpeechSynthesisUtterance is a JavaScript object
 used in the Web Speech API to convert text into voice.



